title: HOUR 1- Kirk Herbstreit Sep 16, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 1- Kirk Herbstreit Sep 16, 2020
description:
Kirk Herbstreit gives Dan his opinion on the return of Big 10 football. Kirk tells Dan that he does not see Dabo Sweeney going to the NFL. Kirk says Dabo would give up so much power by coaching in the NFL.
